{"data": [{"id": "4742294", "title": "Wall Street Breakfast Podcast: Bitcoin Tops $100K, Trump Picks Crypto Ally", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Crypto currency and digital wallets concept background. Futuristic bitcoin icon in world of technological progress and innovation. CGI 3D render\" data-id=\"2149225006\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">da-kuk</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div></p> <p>Listen below or on the go on <a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/wall-street-breakfast/id1358381502?mt=2\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apple Podcasts</a> and <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/05uLjJxkVgQsRk8LWLCLpx?si=r3_yJgxiQiivJwNQG8WNew&amp;nd=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">Spotify</a></p> <p><div class=\"pcast hidden-print\">\n  <div class=\"pcast__section-1\">\n    <img alt=\"\" class=\"pcast__top-img pcast__marketing\" src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2018/11/21/podcast_series_header.png\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pcast__section-2\"><iframe src=\"https://widget.spreaker.com/player?episode_id=63163885&amp;theme=light&amp;playlist=false&amp;playlist-continuous=false&amp;chapters-image=true&amp;episode_image_position=right&amp;hide-logo=true&amp;hide-likes=true&amp;hide-comments=true&amp;hide-sharing=true&amp;hide-download=true&amp;color=ff6900\" width=\"100%\" height=\"200px\" frameborder=\"0\" sap-id=\"4\"></iframe></div>\n  <div class=\"pcast__section-3\">\n    <div class=\"pcast__ad-container\"></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</p> <p>Bitcoin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BTC-USD\" title=\"Bitcoin USD\">BTC-USD</a>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4364445-bitcoin-crosses-100000-as-trump-picks-crypto-backer-paul-atkins-for-sec-chair-powell-comments\">crosses $100,000</a> as Trump picks crypto backer, Paul Atkins for SEC chair, Powell comments. (00:24) Shell (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SHEL\" title=\"Shell plc\">SHEL</a>), Equinor (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EQNR\" title=\"Equinor ASA\">EQNR</a>) to <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4364749-shell-equinor-joint-venture-uk-north-sea-oil-gas\">combine assets</a> to form UK's biggest independent oil and gas firm. (01:34) Amazon (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMZN\" title=\"Amazon.com, Inc.\">AMZN</a>) sued for <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4364750-amazon-lawsuit-allegedly-excluding-dc-zip-codes-prime-delivery-benefits\">allegedly excluding</a> D.C. zip codes from Prime delivery benefits. (02:20)</p> <p>This is an abridged transcript of the podcast.</p> <p>Bitcoin has finally managed to cross the $100,000 milestone mark as the cryptocurrency continues to see a meteoric rise after Donald Trump's win.</p> <p>The world's oldest cryptocurrency has risen ~45% since Election Day.</p> <p>At last check, Bitcoin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BTC-USD\" title=\"Bitcoin USD\">BTC-USD</a>) is trading 6.5% higher at $103,189.</p> <p>The crypto rally was further fueled by the nomination of cryptocurrency advocate Paul Atkins to chair the Securities and Exchange Commission.</p> <p>The President-Elect wrote on Truth Social that Atkins \u201cbelieves in the promise of robust, innovative capital markets that are responsive to the needs of Investors, &amp; that provide capital to make our Economy the best in the World. He also recognizes that digital assets &amp; other innovations are crucial to Making America Greater than Ever Before.\u201d</p> <p>Paul Atkins will replace Gary Gensler, who has been leading the U.S. government\u2019s crackdown on the crypto industry, during the Biden regime. Gensler announced last month that he would be stepping down from his post on the day that Trump is inaugurated \u2014 Jan. 20, 2025.</p> <p>British oil giant Shell (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SHEL#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link%7Cfirst_level_url%3Anews\">SHEL</a>) and Norway's state-run energy firm Equinor (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EQNR#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link%7Cfirst_level_url%3Anews\">EQNR</a>) will combine their U.K. offshore oil and gas assets to form a new company that will be the U.K.'s largest independent oil and gas producer.</p> <p>The 50-50 joint venture is aimed at sustaining domestic oil and gas production and security of energy supply in the U.K. at a time when the U.K. North Sea basin is maturing and production is naturally declining.</p> <p>A range of exploration licenses will also be part of the deal, the companies said in a statement. The JV is expected to produce over 140,000 barrels of oil equivalent per day in 2025.</p> <p>The <a href=\"https://www.shell.com/news-and-insights/newsroom/news-and-media-releases/2024/shell-and-equinor-to-create-the-uk-largest-independent-oil-and-gas-company.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">transaction</a>, which has economic effect on January 1, is expected to be completed by the end of 2025.</p> <p>Amazon (NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMZN#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link%7Cfirst_level_url%3Anews\">AMZN</a>) has been sued by Washington, D.C.'s attorney general for secretly excluding around 48,000 customers in low-income neighborhoods from its high-speed delivery service Prime while continuing to charge them the full subscription price.</p> <p>D.C. Attorney General Brian Schwalb alleged that Amazon (NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMZN#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link%7Cfirst_level_url%3Anews\">AMZN</a>) excluded Prime members in two zip codes (20019, 20020) east of the Anacostia River - \"historically underserved communities\" - from the fast delivery service since 2022.</p> <p>The e-commerce giant instead has been servicing those zip codes with third-party delivery services like UPS (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UPS\" title=\"United Parcel Service, Inc.\">UPS</a>) and the U.S. Postal Service, \"which it knows are often slower than Amazon's,\" the lawsuit read.</p> <p>It added that Amazon (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMZN\" title=\"Amazon.com, Inc.\">AMZN</a>) claims to have made \"this secret change\" in delivery options based on concerns over driver safety in the zip codes. But the company allegedly failed to be transparent about its decision.</p> <p>\"While Amazon (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMZN\" title=\"Amazon.com, Inc.\">AMZN</a>) has every right to make operational changes, it cannot covertly decide that a dollar in one zip code is worth less than a dollar in another,\" <a href=\"https://oag.dc.gov/release/attorney-general-schwalb-sues-amazon-secretly\" rel=\"nofollow\">said</a> Schwalb. \"We're suing to stop this deceptive conduct and make sure District residents get what they're paying for.\"</p> <p>More articles on Seeking Alpha:</p> <p><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4364209-meta-to-build-10b-ai-data-center-in-louisiana-to-work-with-entergy-for-energy-needs\">Meta to build $10B AI data center in Louisiana, to work with Entergy for energy needs</a></p> <p><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4364745-vodafone-uk-three-uk-merger-gets-an-all-clear-with-conditions-from-cma\">Vodafone UK - Three UK merger gets an all-clear, with conditions from CMA</a></p> <p><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4363797-hershey-suitors-have-been-rebuffed-hard-to-buy-chocolate-maker-analyst\">Hershey suitors have been rebuffed, hard to buy chocolate maker - analyst</a></p> <p><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4363973-teamsters-union-files-charges-against-costco-alleging-unfair-labour-practices\">Teamsters union files charges against Costco, alleging unfair labour practices</a></p> <p>Catalyst watch:</p> <ul> <li><p>OPEC+ talks on output.</p></li> <li><p>Markforged (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MKFG\" title=\"Markforged Holding Corporation\">MKFG</a>) shareholders vote on sale to Nano Dimension (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NNDM\" title=\"Nano Dimension Ltd.\">NNDM</a>)</p></li> <li><p>CoStar Group (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CSGP\" title=\"CoStar Group, Inc.\">CSGP</a>) investor day</p></li> <li><p>Tractor Supply (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSCO\" title=\"Tractor Supply Company\">TSCO</a>) investor day</p></li> </ul> <p>Now let\u2019s take a look at the markets as of 6 am. Ahead of the opening bell today, Dow, S&amp;P and Nasdaq futures are in the red. Crude oil is up 0.5% at $68/barrel.</p> <p>In the world markets, the FTSE 100 is flat and the DAX is up 0.4%.</p> <p>The <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4364757-biggest-stock-movers-thursday-crypto-stocks-aeo-and-more\">biggest movers</a> for the day premarket: American Eagle Outfitters (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AEO\" title=\"American Eagle Outfitters, Inc.\">AEO</a>) is down 14% following mixed FQ3 results, missing revenue expectations and cutting its full-year outlook.</p> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div><p>On today\u2019s economic calendar:</p> <ul> <li><p>8:30 am International Trade in Goods and Services</p></li> <li><p>10:30 am EIA Natural Gas Report</p></li> <li><p>12:15 pm Richmond Federal Reserve Bank President Thomas Barkin to speak before in-person Charlotte Regional Business Alliance 2024 Economic Outlook event.</p></li> </ul>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149225006/image_2149225006.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742294-wall-street-breakfast-podcast-bitcoin-tops-100k-trump-picks-crypto-ally", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 14:33:39"}, {"id": "4742284", "title": "Palantir Technologies: Correction Is Likely Coming", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426101020/image_1426101020.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Palantir Technologies\" data-id=\"1426101020\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">hapabapa</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>My Thesis Update</h2> <p>I initiated coverage of <strong>Palantir Technologies Inc.</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PLTR\" title=\"Palantir Technologies Inc.\">PLTR</a></span>) stock back in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4662863-palantir-stock-this-dip-is-gift-buy\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4662863-palantir-stock-this-dip-is-gift-buy\" target=\"_blank\">January 2024</a> with a \"Buy\" rating, reiterating it 6 months ago <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4682977-palantir-stock-no-dip-no-problem\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4682977-palantir-stock-no-dip-no-problem\" target=\"_blank\">on April 9, 2024</a>. Since the publication of my April article, the</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742284-palantir-technologies-stock-correction-likely-coming", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 14:31:09"}, {"id": "4742281", "title": "Operating Leverage Is Boosting Carvana Faster Than Previously Expected (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1032106908/image_1032106908.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Growing investment concept\" data-id=\"1032106908\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1032106908/image_1032106908.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1032106908/image_1032106908.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1032106908/image_1032106908.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1032106908/image_1032106908.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1032106908/image_1032106908.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1032106908/image_1032106908.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1032106908/image_1032106908.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1032106908/image_1032106908.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Ghing/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The <a href=\"https://www.fasb.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Financial Accounting Standards Board</a> (FASB) has been missing the ball.</p> <p>This is the organization that establishes Generally Accepted Accounting Principles (GAAP). That set of rules tells public corporations how to compute and present the numbers upon</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1032106908/image_1032106908.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742281-operating-leverage-is-boosting-carvana-faster-than-previously-expected-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 14:23:18"}, {"id": "4742280", "title": "Hims & Hers Vs. Amazon: Why David Defeats Goliath", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/153701304/image_153701304.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"David and Goliath on the house wall ,Regensburg,unesco heritage\" data-id=\"153701304\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1021px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/153701304/image_153701304.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/153701304/image_153701304.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/153701304/image_153701304.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/153701304/image_153701304.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/153701304/image_153701304.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/153701304/image_153701304.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/153701304/image_153701304.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/153701304/image_153701304.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">kaetana_istock</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis Summary</h2> <p><strong>Hims &amp; Hers</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HIMS\" title=\"Hims &amp; Hers Health, Inc.\">HIMS</a></span>) has been on a monster rally in the last year, as it has become a dominant player in the telehealth market.</p> <p>The only real threat to this company, right now, seems to be competition.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/153701304/image_153701304.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742280-hims-and-hers-vs-amazon-why-david-defeats-goliath", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 14:16:30"}, {"id": "4742291", "title": "Is U.S. Economic Growth Accelerating In Q4?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1474796041/image_1474796041.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business and Leadership Success\" data-id=\"1474796041\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1072px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1474796041/image_1474796041.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1474796041/image_1474796041.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1474796041/image_1474796041.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1474796041/image_1474796041.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1474796041/image_1474796041.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1474796041/image_1474796041.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1474796041/image_1474796041.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1474796041/image_1474796041.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">We Are</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The odds still look skewed toward a softer pace of expansion for fourth-quarter GDP, but an upgraded nowcast from the Atlanta Fed hints at the possibility for something stronger.</p> <p>The regional Fed bank\u2019s <a href=\"https://www.atlantafed.org/cqer/research/gdpnow\" rel=\"noopener\">GDPNow model</a> lifted its</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1474796041/image_1474796041.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742291-is-us-economic-growth-accelerating-in-q4", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 14:15:00"}, {"id": "4742286", "title": "A Passive Income Solution Without The Volatility", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1887449055/image_1887449055.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business Professionals in a Meeting Brainstorming Ideas and Discussing Financial Data and Statistics\" data-id=\"1887449055\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1887449055/image_1887449055.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1887449055/image_1887449055.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1887449055/image_1887449055.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1887449055/image_1887449055.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1887449055/image_1887449055.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1887449055/image_1887449055.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1887449055/image_1887449055.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1887449055/image_1887449055.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">LaylaBird</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Kevin Flanagan</em></p> <p>With the U.S. interest rate landscape returning to a more historically normal setting over the last year or so, investors are now presented with a backdrop that hasn't been witnessed in literally more than a decade. As a result, I</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1887449055/image_1887449055.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742286-passive-income-solution-without-volatility", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 13:50:00"}, {"id": "4742285", "title": "What's Next For Global Monetary Policy?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1197543861/image_1197543861.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business consept image Financial graphs\" data-id=\"1197543861\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1197543861/image_1197543861.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1197543861/image_1197543861.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1197543861/image_1197543861.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1197543861/image_1197543861.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1197543861/image_1197543861.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1197543861/image_1197543861.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1197543861/image_1197543861.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1197543861/image_1197543861.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Ca-ssis</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div></p> <p><em>By Erik Norland</em></p> <h2>At a Glance</h2> <ul> <li>Lingering core inflation is complicating central banks' efforts to balance growth and inflation risks</li> <li>Futures curves suggest further rate cuts could be ahead for multiple countries</li> </ul> <p><em>2024 was a global turning point for monetary policy. After two years of massive policy tightening, central banks began to ease policy pretty much across the board. What might be in store for 2025?</em></p> <p><figure class=\"sa-widget sa-embed\" data-id=\"28167\" data-category=\"video\" data-provider=\"Brightcove\" data-thumbnail=\"https://cf-images.us-east-1.prod.boltdns.net/v1/static/49919183001/0f9c1abc-7fe3-4523-a859-7a62b771ce06/c8c23482-1281-47ac-988a-621414d63b04/1280x720/match/image.jpg\"><iframe src=\"https://seekingalpha.com/embed/28167\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" class=\"sa-embed-iframe embed-responsive-item\" data-original-width=\"640\" data-original-height=\"360\" data-id=\"28167\" data-category=\"video\" data-provider=\"Brightcove\"></iframe></figure></p> <p>Going into next year, futures curves for SOFR, Euro ESTR and analogous products on other markets, suggest that traders still see some room for further interest rate reduction in the U.S., the eurozone, the U.K., Australia and Canada. Recently, however, traders have curtailed these expectations for rate cuts.</p> <p><figure class=\"regular-img-figure\" contenteditable=\"false\"><picture><span><a href=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/5/55028208-17333944961917336_origin.png\" rel=\"lightbox\" data-width=\"942\" data-height=\"654\" data-og-image-twitter_small_card=\"true\" data-og-image-twitter_large_card=\"true\" data-og-image-twitter_image_post=\"true\" data-og-image-msn=\"true\" data-og-image-facebook=\"true\" data-og-image-google_news=\"true\" data-og-image-google_plus=\"true\" data-og-image-linkedin=\"true\"><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/5/55028208-17333944961917336.png\" alt=\"interest rate expectations as of nov. 21, 2024\" contenteditable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></span></picture></figure></p> <p>While inflation is way down from its peak levels in 2022 and 2023, it has stopped falling in many countries and remains about 1-2% above pre-pandemic levels.</p> <p><figure class=\"regular-img-figure\" contenteditable=\"false\"><picture><span><a href=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/5/55028208-173339452029718_origin.png\" rel=\"lightbox\" data-width=\"947\" data-height=\"658\" data-og-image-twitter_small_card=\"true\" data-og-image-twitter_large_card=\"true\" data-og-image-twitter_image_post=\"true\" data-og-image-msn=\"true\" data-og-image-facebook=\"true\" data-og-image-google_news=\"true\" data-og-image-google_plus=\"true\" data-og-image-linkedin=\"true\"><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2024/12/5/55028208-173339452029718.png\" alt=\"Core Inflation\" contenteditable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></span></picture></figure></p> <p>In the U.S. for example, core inflation has stabilized at around 3.3% for the past six months, while its pre-pandemic level was typically closer to the Fed's target of 2%.</p> <p>This creates a dilemma for the Fed and other central banks. On the one hand, they might like to cut rates further, especially if economic growth slows in response to their policy tightening in 2022 and 2023, which was the largest in over forty years. On the other hand, persistent core inflation might give them pause, especially if further rate cuts risk igniting second rounds of inflation later this decade.</p> <p><a href=\"https://www.cmegroup.com/openmarkets/economics/2024/Whats-Next-for-Global-Monetary-Policy.html?source=rss\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener noopener\">Original Post</a></p> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div><p><strong>Editor's Note:</strong> The summary bullets for this article were chosen by Seeking Alpha editors.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1197543861/image_1197543861.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742285-whats-next-for-global-monetary-policy", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 13:40:00"}, {"id": "4742275", "title": "Teleperformance: Very Interesting Trends, A Continued 'Buy' For Me", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><i