 S&amp;P Quality FCF Aristocrats\u00ae (Free Cash Flow Aristocrats) Indices. Like the S&amp;P Dividend Aristocrats, this new series emphasizes</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/469565348/image_469565348.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742282-comparing-sp-quality-fcf-aristocrats-indices-with-sp-dividend-aristocrats", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 13:30:00"}, {"id": "4742270", "title": "Peloton Interactive: Subscriber Losses And Dilution Create Headwinds", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369193071/image_1369193071.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Man using his indoor bike turbo trainer at home in the evening\" data-id=\"1369193071\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369193071/image_1369193071.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369193071/image_1369193071.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369193071/image_1369193071.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369193071/image_1369193071.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369193071/image_1369193071.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369193071/image_1369193071.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369193071/image_1369193071.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1369193071/image_1369193071.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-ca